#: ../../source/intro.rst:2
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:4
msgid "ImageTrans是一款图片文字转录、图片翻译软件。ImageTrans不同于谷歌的图片自动翻译，它提供人工精调功能，是一款以人为本的辅助工具。"
msgstr "ImageTrans is an image transcription and translation tool. Unlike Google's automatic image translation, it allows users to finely control the translation process."


#: ../../source/intro.rst:6
msgid "功能："
msgstr "Features:"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:8
msgid "自动或者辅助用户框选文字区域，调用多种OCR引擎进行文字识别"
msgstr "Text areas detection (automatic and manual). Supports multiple OCR engines."


#: ../../source/intro.rst:9
msgid "对文字区域排序，并将文字导出为xlsx、docx等多种格式文件"
msgstr "Sort text areas and export the text as xlsx, docx, and other format files"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:10
msgid "调用机器翻译对识别的文字做预翻译"
msgstr "Use machine translation to pre-translate source text"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:11
msgid "调用Photoshop读取PSD文件、导出可编辑的译文PSD文件"
msgstr "Call Photoshop to read PSD files and generate editable translated PSD files"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:12
msgid "设置字体样式"
msgstr "Text Styling"


#: ../../source/intro.rst:13
msgid "针对漫画翻译设计的文字区域检测和文字抹除功能"
msgstr "Text area detection and text erasing designed for comic translation"


